annotationA: CG5276, isoform A; Nucleoside-triphosphatase activity; nucleoside-diphosphatase activity; calcium ion binding
annotationB: Nucleoside diphosphate kinase; Major role in the synthesis of nucleoside triphosphates other than ATP. The ATP gamma phosphate is transferred to the NDP beta phosphate via a ping-pong mechanism, using a phosphorylated active-site intermediate
